setSwitchIntervals

public void setSwitchIntervals(double[][] intervals)
Set intervals of time that are to be interpreted as switches. These are converted to FPGA memory cycles before being stored internally. A single timing result will be interpreted as a switch if it lies within any one of these intervals.

Parameters:
intervals -
